title: Los Angeles Snow Globe
description: I acquired this snow globe on a trip to Los Angeles for the Digital Library Federation Forum in Pasadena, California in April of 2007. My friend, Melanie, and I headed to California a few days early to stay with our former boss, Kris, for a few days. During that trip, we went to the Getty, a farmer's market, walked through the UCLA campus, and did other stuff that I don't remember right now. Snow globe (plastic) with the letters "L" and "A" flanked by palm trees.
subject: souvenirs; palm trees;
